text: The Toronto Star is a Canadian broadsheet daily newspaper. As of 2015, it was Canada's highest-circulation newspaper. The Toronto Star is owned by Toronto Star Newspapers Limited, a subsidiary of Torstar Corporation and part of Torstar's Daily News Brands division. ==References== Category:1892 establishments in Canada Category:Newspapers published in Canada Category:English-language newspapers published in Canada Category:Organizations based in Toronto
